settings.nq_title: Take a quiz and get your Parenting style.
settings.title: Your parenting style [parenting_style]
settings.description: Your parenting style is balanced between Permissive-indulgent which means that you rate highly on warmth and engagement with your children but lower on level of control and setting clear limits for them and ‘Hands-off’ which means that you tent to have more laissez-faire of less involved approach to your children.
